'''苋菜红'''（又称'''FD＆C'''、'''Red #2'''、'''E123'''、'''C.I. Food Red 9'''、'''酸性红27'''、'''Azorubin'''、'''S'''或'''CI 16185'''）是一种经修改的[[红色|红色]][[偶氮染料|偶氮染料]]，有[[食用色素|食用色素]]和为[[化妝品|化妝品]]着色的用途。该名称取自苋菜，这种植物以它的红色和可食用的富含蛋白质的种子而著称。

苋菜红是一种阴离子染料。它可以使用于天然和合成的[[纤维|纤维]]、[[皮革|皮革]]、[[纸|纸]]和[[酚醛树脂|酚醛树脂]]。苋菜红用作[[食品添加剂|食品添加剂]]时，其[[E编码|E编码]]为E123。苋菜红通常以三钠[[盐_(化学)|盐]]的形式存在。它是一种棕红色、深红色或紫色的水溶性粉末，在120℃时分解，但不熔化。跟所有偶氮染料一样，苋菜红在20世纪中叶由[[煤焦油|煤焦油]]制成。现代合成物更可能由石油副产品制成。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Amaranth E123|url=http://www.lookcut.com/tools/food-additives/amaranth-e123.html|accessdate=August 15, 2014|date=2004–2010|publisher=LOOKCUT, INC.|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109141158/http://www.lookcut.com/tools/food-additives/amaranth-e123.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Aniline Wood Dye, Coal Tar Dyes|url=http://www.craftsman-style.info/finishing/014-aniline.htm|accessdate=August 15, 2014|date=2005–2012|work=Craftsman Style|publisher=International Styles Network|archive-date=2020-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200725042949/http://www.craftsman-style.info/finishing/014-aniline.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

自1976年以来，[[美国食品药品监督管理局|美国食品药品监督管理局]]（FDA）以可疑[[致癌物|致癌物]]为由禁止使用苋菜红。<ref>{{Citation|quote=Be award that the following color additives are not on the list for use in food products in the United States. a. Amaranth (C.I. 16185, EEC No E123, formerly certifiable as FD&C Red No 2)|url=https://www.fda.gov/downloads/Food/GuidanceComplianceRegulatoryInformation/ComplianceEnforcement/ucm072848.pdf|title=Compliance Program Guidance Manual: Domestic Food Safety (FY07-08)|page=6|publisher=[[Food_and_Drug_Administration|Food and Drug Administration]]|date=November 9, 2008|accessdate=2020-11-09|archive-date=2017-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170215171030/http://www.fda.gov/downloads/Food/GuidanceComplianceRegulatoryInformation/ComplianceEnforcement/ucm072848.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Citation|title=Color Additives Fact Sheet|publisher=[[Food_and_Drug_Administration_(United_States)|U. S. Food and Drug Administration]]'s Center for Food Safety and Applied Nutrition|date=July 30, 2001|url=http://www.cfsan.fda.gov/~dms/cos-221.html|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20011117164702/http://www.cfsan.fda.gov/~dms/cos-221.html|archivedate=November 17, 2001}}</ref><ref>{{Citation|title=OVERVIEW OF FOOD COLOR ADDITIVES, Prepared for the USDA National Organic Program and the National Organic Standards Board|date=October 14, 2005|pages=1 and 7|publisher=[[Agricultural_Marketing_Service|Agricultural Marketing Service]] ([[United_States_Department_of_Agriculture|United States Department of Agriculture]])|url=http://www.ams.usda.gov/AMSv1.0/getfile?dDocName=STELPRDC5057347|access-date=August 15, 2014|archive-date=2010-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100309133752/http://www.ams.usda.gov/AMSv1.0/getfile?dDocName=STELPRDC5057347|dead-url=no}}</ref>某些国家/地区仍然允许使用它，尤其是在[[英国|英国]]，它最常用于给予[[蜜饯|蜜饯]]樱桃独特的颜色。

在1950年代发生涉及{{le|酸橙20|Acid Orange 20}}的事件以后，<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ob4PAAAAIAAJ&q=FD%26C+Orange+number+1+Halloween+candy&dq=FD%26C+Orange+number+1+Halloween+candy|title=Science News Letter, Volumes 65-66|publisher=Science Service|date=January 30, 1954|page=95|access-date=2020-11-09|archive-date=2020-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200725042623/https://books.google.com/books?id=ob4PAAAAIAAJ&q=FD%26C+Orange+number+1+Halloween+candy&dq=FD%26C+Orange+number+1+Halloween+candy|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Toxicology">{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=zqLLa-MI8k0C&printsec=frontcover&dq=Toxicology+Omaye&q=Amaranth|title=Food and Nutritional Toxicology|first=Stanley T.|last=Omaye|page=257|publisher=CRC Press LLC|year=2004|isbn=0-203-48530-0|access-date=2020-11-09|archive-date=2020-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200725041933/https://books.google.com/books?id=zqLLa-MI8k0C&printsec=frontcover&dq=Toxicology+Omaye&q=Amaranth|dead-url=no}}</ref>FDA重新检验了食用色素。1960年，FDA被授予对颜色添加剂的管辖权，并限制可以添加到食品中的数量。它也要求食品色素的生产者确保色素的安全性和正确的标签。它暂时允许使用食品添加剂，如果出现安全问题，可以随时取消。FDA对已在使用的物质给予“[[公认安全|公认安全]]”（GRAS）临时状态，并将苋菜红的临时状态延长了14倍。

1971年，一项苏联研究将这种染料与癌症联系起来。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Why Red M&M's Disappeared for a Decade|url=https://priceonomics.com/why-red-mandms-disappeared-for-a-decade/|accessdate=2016-08-16|date=|publisher=Pricenomics|quote=|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108091122/https://priceonomics.com/why-red-mandms-disappeared-for-a-decade/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Toxicology">{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=zqLLa-MI8k0C&printsec=frontcover&dq=Toxicology+Omaye&q=Amaranth|title=Food and Nutritional Toxicology|first=Stanley T.|last=Omaye|page=257|publisher=CRC Press LLC|year=2004|isbn=0-203-48530-0}}</ref>截至1976年，超过{{Convert|1000000|lb}}（价值500万美元）的苋菜红使用于价值10十亿美元的食品、药品和化妆品。美国的消费主义者认为FDA和食品集团在勾结<ref name="NewSci">{{Cite journal|title=Washington View: FDA in difficulties|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=0C1mPFyQYloC&pg=PA600&dq=Alexander+Schmidt+FDA+no+evidence&q=Alexander%20Schmidt%20FDA%20no%20evidence|last=Greenberg|first=Dan|date=4 December 1975|journal=New Scientist|publisher=New Science Publications|issue=978|location=London|volume=64|page=600|access-date=2020-11-09|archive-date=2020-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120094055/https://books.google.com/books?id=0C1mPFyQYloC&pg=PA600&dq=Alexander+Schmidt+FDA+no+evidence&q=Alexander%20Schmidt%20FDA%20no%20evidence|dead-url=no}}</ref>，因此感到不安，于是逼迫FDA禁止它。尽管有所有证据，FDA专员亚历山大·施密特（Alexander Schmidt）还是为染料辩护，指出FDA发现“没有任何危害公共健康的证据”。FDA的实验表明，雌性大鼠服用高剂量的苋菜红，恶性肿瘤的发生率便会显着增加，并得出结论，由于不能再假定安全，应停止使用该染料。FDA在1976年禁止苋菜红。<ref name="time">{{Cite news|first=|author=|authorlink=|title=Death of a Dye|url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,945520,00.html|work=[[Time_magazine|TIME magazine]]|date=February 2, 1976|accessdate=2009-07-07|archive-date=2010-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100404162345/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,945520,00.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|first=|author=|authorlink=|title=Burger Backs Red Dye Ban Pending Rule|url=https://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/courant/access/959307712.html?dids=959307712:959307712&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:AI&date=Feb+14%2C+1976&author=&pub=The+Hartford+Courant&desc=Burger+Backs+Red+Dye+Ban+Pending+Rule&pqatl=google|work=[[The_Hartford_Courant|The Hartford Courant]]|date=February 14, 1976|accessdate=2009-07-07|archive-date=2012-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121021133151/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/courant/access/959307712.html?dids=959307712:959307712&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:AI&date=Feb+14,+1976&author=&pub=The+Hartford+Courant&desc=Burger+Backs+Red+Dye+Ban+Pending+Rule&pqatl=google|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[诱惑红|诱惑红]]取代了遭受禁止的苋菜红。

